{"tid":2354295,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中年漢一句「X你老母死差佬」罪成上訴得直 官：支持警察者有時也會失控罵警","createTime":"2021-01-05T11:12:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T11:55:47.000Z","uid":5195,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"20849a2bcf5cc88cc8998bb8849d077f84804b3e","tid":2354295,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T11:12:22.000Z","msg":"中年漢途經示威現場，因一句「X你老母死差佬，我頭先無啦啦食咗兩粒催淚彈」，被裁定擾亂秩序罪成。高等法院早前判他上訴得直，今頒下判詞。對於原審裁判官覺得被告自辯時突稱遭警方舉槍相向和用強光照射，但同時又自稱支持警察，實屬信口雌黃，自相矛盾；高院法官黃崇厚則指，支持警察的人有時也可失控辱罵警員。此外，法官查詢後發現辯方大律師知悉強光情節，卻沒用以盤問證人，而裁判官不知被告曾向律師交代情節，評估被告誠信時依賴了不準確資料，定罪不穩妥。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210105/6VO2R6IRF5HNNOFNLRJYLQXLRE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210105%2F6VO2R6IRF5HNNOFNLRJYLQXLRE%2F&d=QL2FFPepynYtbGyOTzoAG9fEBUFsnbtb5M0%2Bd5EIgxU%3D&h=4225311f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210105%2F6VO2R6IRF5HNNOFNLRJYLQXLRE%2F&h=98164743\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210105/6VO2R6IRF5HNNOFNLRJYLQXLRE/</a>"},{"pid":"8333290fa913f59119455c706af7f33029cf2e80","tid":2354295,"uid":47356,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T11:14:25.000Z","msg":"X你老母死差佬"},{"pid":"cd0f1baa1e726300b242c6a8e6ed0ea269517856","tid":2354295,"uid":54593,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T11:16:13.000Z","msg":"藍屍罵警無罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae583218f6e4cb6b35a5fea6ddcf12fe562c9185","tid":2354295,"uid":103719,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T11:17:04.000Z","msg":"啱啊dllm死黑警<br />\n利申 撐警"},{"pid":"54af8dacb3af2b4989549e58afb4173eb90644db","tid":2354295,"uid":29042,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"cd0f1baa1e726300b242c6a8e6ed0ea269517856","tid":2354295,"uid":54593,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T11:16: